      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">ICU rooms maintained under negative pressure relative to adjacent areas; evaluated for aerosol containment, decay behavior, distribution patterns, and reduced exfiltration. | Clinical rooms maintained under negative pressure. The conclusion states that these rooms effectively eliminated aerosols, indicating their role in aerosol removal or containment in healthcare settings.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.88</data>
