      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">One of the studied ICU rooms. ICU 1 was tested in both positive and negative pressure configurations, enabling comparison of pressure-dependent airflow and aerosol movement. | Specific ICU room compared with ICU3. It has a nearly identical layout to ICU3 and was evaluated through air-change-rate and aerosol decay-rate comparisons, especially in negative pressure mode.</data>
