      <data key="d0">AEROSOL PROPAGATION TREND AT UWMC</data>
      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">The aerosol movement trend observed or inferred at UWMC from plume tracing experiments. The text notes that additional aerosol plume tracing experiments would help generalize this propagation trend across the hospital environment.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.76</data>
      <data key="d4">62e55c5d-3b2a-4772-a671-df2065fce8b1_chunk_36</data>
      <data key="d5">62e55c5d-3b2a-4772-a671-df2065fce8b1</data>
