      <data key="d0">HVAC OR OTHER FILTRATION UNITS</data>
      <data key="d1">HVAC_UNIT</data>
      <data key="d2">Building ventilation or filtration systems referenced as mechanisms that may remove aerosol particles. Particle size information could help estimate whether particles settle or are removed by HVAC or filtration units.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.66</data>
      <data key="d4">62e55c5d-3b2a-4772-a671-df2065fce8b1_chunk_36</data>
