      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Facilities with open floor plans referenced in prior work on infectious aerosol persistence. Aerosols generated in these settings were described as remaining largely localized to the operatory rather than spreading significantly beyond it.</data>
