      <data key="d1">TRACER_GAS</data>
      <data key="d2">A simulated aerosol medium used in procedures discussed in the text to evaluate aerosol spread. Although NaCl aerosol is not literally a gas, it functions here as a tracer-like medium within the available schema for tracking aerosol movement.</data>
