      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">A specialized intensive care unit referenced in a study of HVAC-system effects on infectious aerosol dispersion. In this zone, inlet and outlet grid position and ventilation flow rate were reported to contribute to uneven aerosol distribution.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
      <data key="d4">62e55c5d-3b2a-4772-a671-df2065fce8b1_chunk_39,62e55c5d-3b2a-4772-a671-df2065fce8b1_chunk_78</data>
