      <data key="d0">ADDITIONAL PORTABLE AIR-EXTRACTION UNIT</data>
      <data key="d1">HVAC_UNIT</data>
      <data key="d2">A portable air-handling or extraction unit whose positioning in the negative-pressure ICU was reported to increase aerosol extraction by 40% after 45 seconds. It modifies room airflow and removal of cough-generated airborne particles.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
      <data key="d4">62e55c5d-3b2a-4772-a671-df2065fce8b1_chunk_39</data>
