      <data key="d0">INLET AND OUTLET GRIDS</data>
      <data key="d1">AIR_PATH</data>
      <data key="d2">Air supply and exhaust or return pathways whose positions were identified as important determinants of aerosol distribution in the room. Their placement, together with ventilation flow rate, can lead to spatially uneven aerosol concentrations.</data>
