      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">Time-dependent airflow and particle-transport patterns generated using transient Lattice Boltzmann Method simulations and compared with Schlieren experiments. These patterns describe how air movement governs airborne particle dispersion in a negative-pressure ICU.</data>
