      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">The transient movement of airborne particles produced by a cough in a negative-pressure ICU. It represents the simulated dispersion, transport, and removal behavior of potentially infectious aerosols.</data>
