      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">An airflow or particle-transport pattern generated by corona discharge, referenced in relation to the behavior of ultrafine particles. Although presented in an aerosol-science context rather than a specific hospital room, it is relevant to understanding how induced air movement can affect airborne particle transport.</data>
