      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">The enclosed hospital elevator compartment modeled as the study zone for evaluating CO2 accumulation, airflow behavior, and cough-generated droplet dispersion under different ventilation strategies.</data>
