      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">Human occupants whose coughing, breathing, or exhalation can introduce respiratory droplets and aerosols carrying infectious pathogens into indoor air. | Human occupants whose coughing or exhalation generates respiratory droplets in the modeled indoor environment.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.78</data>
      <data key="d4">c3ec75c5-6024-45ba-a0b0-8dd0c746991b_chunk_1</data>
