      <data key="d2">A fan is described as the airflow-generating device in the study cases. The text distinguishes downward-blowing and upward-blowing fan configurations, which were analyzed separately using proposed linear regressions.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.63</data>
      <data key="d4">c3ec75c5-6024-45ba-a0b0-8dd0c746991b_chunk_39</data>
