      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">A no-active-ventilation condition abbreviated as NF. Although it represents absence of mechanical ventilation rather than a supplied airflow pattern, it functions as a comparison air-distribution condition in the listed terminology.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.66</data>
      <data key="d4">c3ec75c5-6024-45ba-a0b0-8dd0c746991b_chunk_42</data>
