      <data key="d0">EXHALED BREATH AIR PATH</data>
      <data key="d1">AIR_PATH</data>
      <data key="d2">The expiratory airflow route through which respiratory viruses and aerosol particles may be emitted from an infected person into the surrounding air.</data>
