      <data key="d0">COACH BUS CABIN</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Indoor passenger compartment of a coach bus where pathogen-laden expiratory droplet transmission was studied. It is typed as a zone because the schema only provides HOSPITAL_ZONE for enclosed occupied spaces.</data>
