      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Indoor space implied by the experimental and transient CFD study on temperature effects, velocity fields, and airborne sneeze-droplet transmission. It is represented as a zone in the available schema. | The indoor room environment where aerosol release, airflow following, and distributed absorber measurements were performed.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.82</data>
