      <data key="d1">AIRBORNE_PATHOGEN</data>
      <data key="d2">Respiratory pathogen refers to infectious material emitted through respiratory activity, as cited in the article on turbulent gas clouds and respiratory pathogen emissions. It represents airborne infectious agents transported by exhaled flows.</data>
