      <data key="d0">CLASSROOM / LARGE UNIVERSITY CLASSROOM</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Indoor classroom spaces are the modeled environments in the cited studies, including a classroom where CO2 reduction and thermal comfort were studied and a large university classroom where thermofluid dynamics and droplet transport were evaluated. Although not a hospital space, it is represented as a zone because the valid schema uses HOSPITAL_ZONE for indoor spaces.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.9</data>
