      <data key="d1">AIRBORNE_PATHOGEN</data>
      <data key="d2">The COVID-19 study context is best represented as SARS-CoV-2-laden aerosols and droplets rather than the disease label alone. These infectious particles are relevant to aerodynamic evaluation, social distancing, indoor airflow, and droplet transport in classroom or indoor environments.</data>
