      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Indoor event spaces or venues evaluated for airborne transmission risk. The text discusses limitations in assuming steady-state concentration across these spaces and notes that only a few positions were experimentally covered.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.82</data>
