      <data key="d1">AIRBORNE_PATHOGEN</data>
      <data key="d2">Airborne infectious agent associated with COVID-19 outbreaks and transmission risk in shared indoor environments, used here as the pathogen-risk context for concentration and exposure assessment.</data>
