      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">The number and contact behavior of people during an event, including the presence of an infectious person and their additional contacts during the infectious period, which affects epidemic-growth estimation.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.79</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_42</data>
      <data key="d5">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
