      <data key="d0">BACKGROUND REGIONS</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Modeled indoor regions where unsteady-event correction factors may be especially relevant, particularly for low-air-change cases such as NVV.</data>
