      <data key="d0">DENSE OCCUPANCY HEAT LOAD</data>
      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">The high-occupancy condition in an event location that makes constant thermal boundary conditions critical because occupants contribute heat loads and affect environmental boundary conditions.</data>
