      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">Occupant activity and respiratory condition used as a low-emission scenario in SARS-CoV-2 airborne risk modeling. Aganovic et al. report an estimated quanta emission rate of 0.01 quanta h−1 for a resting occupant who is only breathing at the predicted 35th percentile.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.82</data>
