      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">Study-derived infected-occupant source scenario for university-campus transmission risk. The median SARS-CoV-2 quanta emission rate was estimated between 20 and 454 quanta h⁻¹.</data>
