      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">Infected-occupant source condition characterized by standing posture and speaking. Mikszewski et al. reported a median SARS-CoV-2 emission rate of 2.7 quanta h⁻¹ and a 95th percentile of 250 quanta h⁻¹ for this emitter condition.</data>
