      <data key="d0">SARS-COV-2 RESTING-AND-ORAL-BREATHING EMITTER</data>
      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">Lower-activity infected-occupant source condition characterized by resting and oral breathing. Mikszewski et al. reported a median SARS-CoV-2 emission rate of 0.55 quanta h⁻¹ and a 95th percentile of 52 quanta h⁻¹ for this condition.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.76</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_46</data>
      <data key="d5">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
