      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">Referenced SARS-CoV-2 outbreak source scenarios with above-average quanta emission rates, generally between the 73rd and 98th percentile of the standing-and-speaking emitter distribution, corresponding to approximately 15 to 970 quanta h⁻¹, with one exception outside the predicted range.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.82</data>
