    <node id="VENUES WITH MV">
      <data key="d0">VENUES WITH MV</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Indoor venue spaces evaluated under MV, interpreted as mixing ventilation. The text emphasizes that analytical risk assessment was suitable for MV venues but limited by sensitivity to boundary conditions and room parameters. | Indoor venue spaces evaluated under NV, interpreted as natural ventilation. The text states that prediction of highly exposed positions is difficult in these venues because airflow is strongly affected by boundary conditions and room parameters such as windows.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.88</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_47</data>
