      <data key="d6">VENUES WITH NV</data>
    </node>
    <node id="UNVENTILATED AREAS">
      <data key="d0">UNVENTILATED AREAS</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Areas without effective ventilation where infectious aerosols can accumulate. The text identifies these areas as locations where infection risk can increase locally.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.89</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_47</data>
      <data key="d5">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
    </node>
    <node id="VENUE-SPECIFIC HIGH-RISK SITES">
      <data key="d0">VENUE-SPECIFIC HIGH-RISK SITES</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Locations within venues where individual infection risk is elevated. The text states that these sites vary with ventilation strategy, emitter position, and emission mode, and that they require experimental and numerical assessment to identify reliably.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.91</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_47</data>
      <data key="d5">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
    </node>
    <node id="HIGH-RISK POSITIONS BEYOND PHYSICAL DISTANCE GUIDELINES">
      <data key="d0">HIGH-RISK POSITIONS BEYOND PHYSICAL DISTANCE GUIDELINES</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Elevated-risk positions located farther from the emitter than standard physical-distance guidance would imply. The text notes that high-risk positions were observed well beyond physical-distance guideline ranges at all venues.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.82</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_47</data>
      <data key="d5">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
