      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">An unfavorable airflow condition in which ventilation is insufficient or stagnant. The text associates poor circulation with venue-specific high-risk areas and local aerosol accumulation.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.82</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_47</data>
