      <data key="d1">TRACER_GAS</data>
      <data key="d2">Evaporated NaCl nuclei produced from a 10% NaCl-water aerosol; used as an airborne virus surrogate that follows room airflow. Although particulate rather than gaseous, it functions as the tracer medium in the described ventilation and dispersion measurements.</data>
