      <data key="d0">EVENT VENUE</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Indoor venue where aerosol and airflow measurements were conducted. Although the text describes public venues rather than hospitals, this is typed as HOSPITAL_ZONE because it is the closest valid spatial-zone category.</data>
