      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">Experimental human-occupancy proxy distributed throughout the venue to simulate body-generated buoyancy effects. Each heat source mimicked approximately 80 W of human heat emission, representing thermal plumes produced by seated occupants.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.82</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_52</data>
