      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">The spatial pattern of aerosol movement and airflow in the venue. It was influenced by human-equivalent heat sources, spectators, and body-generated buoyancy effects, and it determined exposure conditions for absorbers.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.88</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_52</data>
      <data key="d5">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
