      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">Thermally driven upward air movement generated by human heat emission or simulated heat sources. These buoyancy effects were specifically simulated to evaluate their influence on aerosol distribution and airflow characteristics.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.76</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_52</data>
      <data key="d5">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
