      <data key="d1">TRACER_GAS</data>
      <data key="d2">Sodium chloride tracer material used experimentally to quantify inhaled mass at absorbers. Although NaCl is an aerosol rather than a gas, it is typed as TRACER_GAS because it serves the valid tracer role for measuring airborne transport and exposure.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.8</data>
      <data key="d4">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_52</data>
