      <data key="d1">AIRBORNE_PATHOGEN</data>
      <data key="d2">A pathogenic microorganism named as a UV-LED inactivation target in the cited Water Research study. Legionella pneumophila is especially relevant to built-environment and healthcare infection control because it can be aerosolized from engineered water systems and inhaled.</data>
