      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">Enclosed occupied compartment used as the modeled public-transport environment. Although not a hospital space, it functions as the indoor zone in which ventilation-driven airflow and pathogen-containing respiratory particle dispersion are simulated.</data>
