      <data key="d2">General class of pathogenic biological agents that may be carried by emitted respiratory particles. These agents represent the broader biological hazard considered in the dispersion scenario, beyond COVID-19 specifically. | Droplets or particles produced by the infected breathing manikin and tracked over space and time inside the coach.</data>
