      <data key="d0">HOSPITAL ROOM</data>
      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">A semi-confined, ventilated clinical space explicitly cited as one of the settings to which the validated CFD airflow and particle-dispersion models could be applied. It is relevant for assessing airborne infectious contamination risk under different ventilation, occupancy, and source-emission conditions.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.78</data>
      <data key="d4">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_1</data>
