      <data key="d0">OCCUPANT LOAD INCLUDING INFECTED PERSON</data>
      <data key="d1">OCCUPANCY_LOAD</data>
      <data key="d2">The group of occupants in the modeled ventilated space, explicitly including an infected person. This load contributes both heat-driven airflow effects and the infectious aerosol source generated by breathing.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.84</data>
      <data key="d4">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_1</data>
      <data key="d5">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42</data>
