      <data key="d1">AIR_PATH</data>
      <data key="d2">Routes by which pathogens are transmitted through air; the text emphasizes the need to understand these routes to slow or stop epidemic spread. | Airborne exposure pathway emphasized during short-term events, where pathogen-laden aerosols move directly from an emitting person toward a susceptible recipient.</data>
