      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">The enclosed occupied compartment used as the CFD simulation domain. Although it is a public-transport space rather than a hospital area, it is treated as the bounded indoor zone where ventilation airflow, passenger occupancy, and pathogen-laden droplet dispersion are evaluated. | The enclosed railway passenger carriage used as the primary modeled ventilation and airflow domain. Although not a hospital space, it is typed as a zone because the schema provides HOSPITAL_ZONE as the available enclosed-zone category.</data>
