      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">High-speed train coach configuration investigated experimentally and numerically by Wang et al. for airflow characteristics and thermal comfort, with air distributed from the ceiling above the central aisle toward lower regions at the coach ends.</data>
