      <data key="d1">AIR_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d2">The spatial movement and organization of air within indoor environments. The text notes that overly simplified ventilation models may fail to predict these patterns accurately, leading to incorrect aerosol-dispersion distributions.</data>
