      <data key="d1">HOSPITAL_ZONE</data>
      <data key="d2">The broader class of occupied indoor spaces for which whole-room far-UVC is being evaluated as an airborne infection-control intervention. The study emphasizes that occupied-room conditions differ from controlled benchtop or chamber settings because airflow and occupant presence can affect airborne virus behavior.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.72</data>
      <data key="d4">d8e5e6fb-91d7-40aa-8229-b92309abbaff_chunk_0</data>
