      <data key="d0">DROPLET AND AEROSOL TRANSMISSION PATHWAY</data>
      <data key="d1">AIR_PATH</data>
      <data key="d2">The airborne and droplet route by which SARS-CoV-2 transmission risk was investigated during the experimental indoor mass gathering event.</data>
      <data key="d3">0.82</data>
      <data key="d4">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d_chunk_0</data>
      <data key="d5">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d</data>
