      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">Zone 2 contributes evidence for the well-mixed condition because PM rises there after the Zone 1 peak declines, showing aerosol redistribution through the room. | Zone 2 participates in the ICU-wide well-mixed condition because its particle concentrations were similar to other ICU locations during the uniform decay phase.</data>
