      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">Greater occupancy increases human-emitted CO2 because more people exhale CO2 into the indoor environment, supporting the use of CO2 monitoring as an occupancy- and ventilation-related indicator.</data>
