      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The lift was evaluated under a non-ventilated no-fan baseline condition, where CO2 accumulated to 35 ppm after 15 s.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.84</data>
