      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The lift was evaluated under an upward-directed airflow condition, which generally lowered CO2 concentration compared with the no-fan case except during the first second. | The lift was evaluated under an upward-blowing ventilation airflow distribution pattern.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.86</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">c3ec75c5-6024-45ba-a0b0-8dd0c746991b_chunk_29</data>
