      <data key="d7">LIFT</data>
      <data key="d8">DOWNWARDS-BLOWING CASE</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The lift was evaluated under a downward-directed airflow condition, which reduced CO2 concentration relative to the no-fan case throughout the reported simulation interval. | The lift was evaluated under a downward-blowing ventilation airflow distribution pattern.</data>
