      <data key="d8">NO FAN CASE</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The lift was evaluated under a no-fan baseline airflow distribution pattern. | The lift is evaluated under a no-fan baseline distribution condition for comparison with fan-driven airflow cases.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.75</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">c3ec75c5-6024-45ba-a0b0-8dd0c746991b_chunk_33</data>
