      <data key="d8">LIFT</data>
      <data key="d9">SERVES</data>
      <data key="d10">The fan serves the lift by supplying ventilation air to the enclosed modeled space. The stated supply velocity through the fan is 6.5 m/s when ventilation is used. | The fan served the lift as the mechanical ventilation unit in the upward-blowing and downward-blowing simulation cases.</data>
