      <data key="d8">CO2</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The two modeled occupants can increase CO2 in the lift through breathing, making CO2 relevant as a tracer of exhaled air and ventilation effectiveness.</data>
