      <data key="d8">LIFT</data>
      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The respiratory openings connect the occupants' breathing and coughing outflows to the lift interior, enabling exhaled air and respiratory material to enter the modeled zone.</data>
