      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The upward- and downward-blowing fan cases are compared as different air-distribution patterns, with similar CO2 decreases during aspiration phases but different exhaust-cycle behavior and cycle regularity.</data>
