      <data key="d9">PATTERN_MEASURED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The no-fan air-distribution scenario is evaluated using time-dependent CO2 concentration, which increases in this case and contributes to the highest reported infection probability.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.78</data>
