      <data key="d8">PATHOGEN-BEARING COUGH DROPLETS</data>
      <data key="d9">PATTERN_MEASURED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The no-fan airflow pattern was assessed by the droplet quantity fraction. Removal started about 1.5 seconds after coughing and took about 2.4 seconds to eliminate roughly 10% of droplets, making it slower than both the downwards-blowing case and the upwards-blowing case for the same early removal amount.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.76</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">c3ec75c5-6024-45ba-a0b0-8dd0c746991b_chunk_32</data>
      <data key="d14">c3ec75c5-6024-45ba-a0b0-8dd0c746991b</data>
