      <data key="d8">PATHOGEN-LADEN EXPIRATORY DROPLETS</data>
      <data key="d9">PATTERN_MEASURED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The no-fan case was compared using droplet elimination behavior and was reported to take the longest time to begin removing droplets.</data>
