      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The infection-probability equation cited in the text is used to calculate infection probability in a closed space, with COVID-19 serving as the referenced airborne infection context in the supporting studies.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.66</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">c3ec75c5-6024-45ba-a0b0-8dd0c746991b_chunk_30</data>
