      <data key="d8">CO2</data>
      <data key="d9">PATTERN_MEASURED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">CO2 concentration is relevant to evaluating gas distribution, but the cited work cautions that the simplified fan approximation is valid for CO2 concentration calculations and not for accurately calculating gas mixing homogeneity.</data>
