      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">A dense indoor live music event increases the opportunity for SARS-CoV-2 exposure and airborne transmission if infectious attendees are present. | An indoor mass-gathering live music event is a high-density occupancy scenario that can increase SARS-CoV-2 transmission risk through crowding and shared indoor air; the cited randomized controlled trial evaluated same-day antigen screening in this setting.</data>
