      <data key="d8">CO2</data>
      <data key="d9">PATTERN_MEASURED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">High-resolution CO2 monitoring is described as a method used to assess ventilation effectiveness and indoor air quality during live theatre and mass gathering events. | Ventilation effectiveness is assessed using high-resolution CO2 monitoring. CO2 provides a measurable indication of accumulated occupant-exhaled air and therefore helps characterize how effectively the indoor space is ventilated.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_7</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
