      <data key="d8">INFECTIOUS AEROSOLS</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The high emitter case represents a 90th-percentile emission condition and therefore increases infectious aerosol release relative to the passive emitter case.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_21</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
