      <data key="d7">VENTILATION PERFORMANCE</data>
      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">ACH_AFFECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">Ventilation performance affects the dilution and removal of SARS-CoV-2-laden aerosols, thereby influencing airborne transmission risk in indoor spaces.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.78</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_8</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
