      <data key="d7">STATIONARY AIRFLOW PATTERNS</data>
      <data key="d8">TRACER GAS</data>
      <data key="d9">PATTERN_MEASURED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">Because stationary airflow patterns are noted as simplified CFD assumptions, tracer-gas measurements can provide experimental evidence to validate or challenge those modeled airflow patterns.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.69</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_9</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
