      <data key="d8">CO2</data>
      <data key="d9">PATTERN_MEASURED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The text lists CO2 among current methodologies used to investigate infectious aerosol distribution in venues, where CO2 can act as a proxy for exhaled-air transport and ventilation effectiveness.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
