      <data key="d8">MIXING VENTILATION</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">MVV2 is also characterized by mixing ventilation and is analyzed alongside MVV and DVV. | MVV2 is a mixing-ventilation condition. Its heterogeneous response to checkerboard seating illustrates that MV airflow can be sensitive to boundary conditions.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_25</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
