      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The full-occupancy baseline of 99 spectators increases the number of exposed occupants in DVV compared with reduced-occupancy scenarios, contributing to the global infection-risk burden.</data>
