      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2 OR COVID-19 AIRBORNE TRANSMISSION CONTEXT</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">Full seating or full occupancy represents the higher-occupancy reference condition. Compared with checkerboard or halved occupancy, it is associated with higher overall propagation-risk values for airborne COVID-19 transmission scenarios in DVV and MVV.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_26</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
    </edge>
