      <data key="d8">INFECTIOUS AEROSOLS</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The infectious person is the occupant source emitting pathogen-bearing aerosols, increasing the presence of infectious aerosols in the indoor environment.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.87</data>
