      <data key="d8">VIRUS VARIANTS WITH INCREASED INFECTIVITY</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">Higher occupancy can increase exposure opportunity for virus variants with increased infectivity, making prolonged events more difficult to control.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.69</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_39</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
    </edge>
