      <data key="d8">DISPLACEMENT VENTILATION</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The venue was evaluated with displacement ventilation as one of the ventilation concepts. In the Omicron example, R &lt; 0.5 for a 3-hour event was achieved in this ventilation condition when surgical masks were used.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.89</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_40</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="VENUE" target="MIXING VENTILATION">
      <data key="d7">VENUE</data>
      <data key="d8">MIXING VENTILATION</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The venue was evaluated with mixing ventilation. For this case, the analytical approach agreed well with the overall airborne infection risk estimated by the other approaches.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.87</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206_chunk_40</data>
      <data key="d14">2c371b3c-bdf6-4d57-aab2-55e74c106206</data>
