      <data key="d8">AUDIENCE AREA</data>
      <data key="d9">SERVES</data>
      <data key="d10">The ventilation system serves the occupied audience area, where the study places one infectious emitter in a fully occupied audience. Ventilation performance in this zone affects dilution and transport of emitted aerosols.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.78</data>
