      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">A single infectious occupant functions as the event source of SARS-CoV-2 emissions, producing airborne exposure used to estimate individual infection probability and global risk or secondary infections.</data>
