      <data key="d9">ACH_AFFECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The air exchange rate affects virus-containing particle concentration by ventilating and diluting shared indoor air. In the equation, λ is in the denominator, so greater AER lowers modeled airborne exposure, especially after adjustment by Ez.</data>
