      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">Under the simple analytical modeling approach, the room is represented using a complete-mixing air distribution assumption.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.73</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a_chunk_14</data>
