      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">Under the high-fidelity CFD modeling approach, the room has a detailed airflow distribution that reflects geometry and spatial airflow patterns.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.86</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a_chunk_14</data>
