      <data key="d8">BULK FLUID FLOW</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The room has an airflow distribution pattern represented by the bulk fluid flow, which governs the modeled particle trajectories and residence times.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a_chunk_16</data>
      <data key="d14">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a</data>
