      <data key="d8">PARTICLE TRAJECTORIES</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The room has particle trajectories that represent the airborne particle movement pattern within the zone and provide the basis for calculating particle residence time and exposure history.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.86</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a_chunk_17</data>
