      <data key="d8">ROOM AIR MIXING</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The measurement facility exhibited room air mixing during the pre-measurement dispersion period, when fans were running and aerosols were allowed to spread throughout the room.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a_chunk_24</data>
