      <data key="d8">TESTING CHAMBER</data>
      <data key="d9">SERVES</data>
      <data key="d10">The fans serve the testing chamber by generating internal airflow that disperses aerosolized SARS-CoV-2 throughout the chamber before UV-C exposure and during the airflow simulation.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.86</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
