      <data key="d8">INITIAL AEROSOL DISPERSION PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d9">SERVES</data>
      <data key="d10">The fans serve the development of the initial aerosol dispersion pattern by operating for about 10 minutes to distribute particles throughout the chamber.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.7</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a_chunk_29</data>
