      <data key="d8">PATHOGEN-CONTAINING AEROSOLS</data>
      <data key="d9">ACH_AFFECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The 0 ACH condition affects pathogen-containing aerosol behavior by providing no mechanical ventilation-driven air exchange, creating a baseline condition for surviving fraction measurements.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a_chunk_24</data>
