      <data key="d8">AEROSOLIZED SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">ACH_AFFECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The 0 ACH condition affects interpretation of aerosolized SARS-CoV-2 survival by eliminating ventilation-driven removal, allowing observed losses under 0% UV conditions to be attributed to effective natural decay.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a_chunk_30</data>
      <data key="d14">19fa3b4e-2c3d-44b1-ae20-59902abc601a</data>
