      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">A possibly infected wearer can exhale bacteria and viruses from the respiratory tract into the immediate environment. The surgical mask is described as a measure intended to limit, rather than create, this spread.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.87</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
