      <data key="d8">VERTICAL DROP AIRFLOW (VDA) SYSTEM</data>
      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The ceiling and floor openings are the physical air paths that make up the VDA system and enable vertical supply and exhaust flow near each seat.</data>
