      <data key="d8">KOREAN HIGH-SPEED TRAIN (KTX) COACH</data>
      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The inlets and outlets connect the ventilation system to the occupied coach air volume, shaping air delivery, exhaust, and particle movement in the compartment.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.88</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_37</data>
