      <data key="d8">RESPIRATORY PARTICLES FROM 3 TO 750 ΜM</data>
      <data key="d9">ACH_AFFECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The doubled air-supply condition affected particle behavior: removal trends were similar, but faster airflow captured and retained particles more strongly.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.89</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_37</data>
