      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The respiratory drops and droplets are described as carriers for viruses such as SARS-CoV-2, thereby increasing the potential airborne viral burden when emitted by an infected occupant.</data>
