      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The controlled simulation domain is used to evaluate thermal phenomena, making anisothermal airflow relevant to the droplet-dispersion behavior around the warm manikin.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.74</data>
