      <data key="d8">BUOYANT PLUMES</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">Including thermal effects in the anisothermal flow model accounts for buoyant plume formation, which influences emitted droplet trajectories and distributions.</data>
