      <data key="d8">PARTICLES CARRYING SARS-COV-2 VIRUS</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The individual is the source of emitted particles carrying pathogenic biological agents, including particles carrying the SARS-CoV-2 virus.</data>
