      <data key="d8">MASK-DEPENDENT PARTICLE DISPERSION PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The pathogen-laden particles exhibit different dispersion patterns depending on whether the individual wears no mask, a perfectly worn mask, or a leaky mask.</data>
