      <data key="d8">THERMALLY DRIVEN AIRFLOW AROUND AND ABOVE THE INDIVIDUAL</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The distribution of pathogen-laden particles is strongly associated with the thermally driven airflow that develops around and above the individual.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.84</data>
      <data key="d12">3</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_40</data>
      <data key="d14">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42</data>
