      <data key="d8">PARALLELEPIPEDIC COMPUTATIONAL DOMAIN</data>
      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The exhaled jet connects the manikin's respiratory outlet to the simulated air volume, introducing warm air and droplets into the computational domain.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.78</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_41</data>
      <data key="d14">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42</data>
