      <data key="d8">ANISOTHERMAL AIRFLOW AND DROPLET DISPERSION PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The no-mask exhalation jet is simulated under anisothermal conditions to show how thermal effects shape the airflow and droplet dispersion pattern.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.84</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_42</data>
