      <data key="d8">ISOTHERMAL AIRFLOW AND DROPLET DISPERSION PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The no-mask exhalation jet is also represented by an isothermal airflow pattern from the prior study, enabling comparison with the anisothermal case.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.72</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_42</data>
