      <data key="d9">ACH_AFFECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The anisothermal airflow and droplet-dispersion pattern affects how SARS-CoV-2-bearing droplets and drops are transported in the modeled space. No ACH value is given, so this relationship captures airflow-pattern influence rather than a quantified air-change-rate effect.</data>
