      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2-CARRYING RESPIRATORY DROPLETS</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The modeled occupant is the emission source for the respiratory droplets carrying SARS-CoV-2 into the coach air.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.79</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_46</data>
      <data key="d14">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="EXHALED AIR PATH" target="SARS-COV-2-LADEN RESPIRATORY DROPLETS">
      <data key="d7">EXHALED AIR PATH</data>
      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2-CARRYING RESPIRATORY DROPLETS</data>
      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The exhaled air path transports the virus-carrying respiratory droplets whose positions are visualized at multiple simulation times.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.86</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_46</data>
      <data key="d14">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="EXHALED AIR PATH" target="ANISOTHERMAL FREE-CONVECTION DISPERSION">
      <data key="d7">EXHALED AIR PATH</data>
      <data key="d8">ANISOTHERMAL FREE-CONVECTION DISPERSION</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">When thermal effects are included, the exhaled airflow and droplets follow a buoyancy-influenced free-convection distribution, especially at reduced exhalation velocity.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.84</data>
      <data key="d12">3</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_46</data>
      <data key="d14">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42</data>
    </edge>
