      <data key="d7">EXHALED AIR PATH</data>
      <data key="d8">ISOTHERMAL AIRFLOW DISPERSION</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">When thermal effects are excluded, the exhaled airflow and droplets follow an isothermal dispersion pattern that differs substantially from the anisothermal case.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.74</data>
      <data key="d12">3</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_46</data>
      <data key="d14">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42</data>
    </edge>
