      <data key="d7">MASK LEAKAGE PATHS AROUND MANIKIN MOUTH</data>
      <data key="d8">CASE #3 SIMULATION DOMAIN</data>
      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">Leakage around the poorly fitting mask provides air paths from the manikin’s mouth region into the simulation domain, allowing more droplets to enter the modeled space.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_48</data>
