      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">When thermal effects are excluded, the pathogen-laden droplets follow the isothermal dispersion pattern, with leakage-origin droplets moving downward, rearward, and sideways.</data>
