      <data key="d8">PASSENGER OPPOSITE THE SPREADER</data>
      <data key="d9">ADJACENT_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The infected manikin/spreader is seated opposite a neighboring passenger, which is relevant because the text notes that the exhaled jet does not directly impact that passenger.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.72</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
