      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">Even when masks are properly worn, some droplets can pass through and remain suspended in the confined coach atmosphere, although the study shows the amount and contamination risk are strongly reduced compared with unmasked passengers.</data>
