      <data key="d8">DISPERSION OF AEROSOLS</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">Recycled air is associated with the aerosol dispersion pattern because the text states that recycling, if not sterilised or effectively filtered, accelerates aerosol dispersion in the coach.</data>
