      <data key="d8">MIXED CONVECTION FLOWS</data>
      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">Ventilation is physically connected to the formation of mixed convection flows because it drives mechanical air movement that combines with buoyancy effects from warm manikins.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_76</data>
      <data key="d14">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42</data>
