      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">Outgoing airflow paths extract air from compartment #1, with extraction adjusted to support end-to-middle airflow. | Outgoing airflow paths extract air from compartment #2, which receives 50% of the total extracted air. | Outgoing airflow paths extract air from compartment #3, with extraction adjusted to support end-to-middle airflow.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.91</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">6ce6bcdd-6339-49d0-abf2-8f8a9a51aa42_chunk_90</data>
