      <data key="d8">TWO AIR CONDITIONING UNITS</data>
      <data key="d9">CONNECTS_TO</data>
      <data key="d10">The return air inlets route returned cabin air back to the air conditioning units, where it mixes with fresh air.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.93</data>
