      <data key="d8">S. AUREUS BIOAEROSOL</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The standing passenger manikin acts as a simulated occupant source that emits S. aureus-containing bioaerosol, increasing the pathogen-containing aerosol load in the modeled indoor environment.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.88</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">92822355-ab82-4e40-9fca-0876f2fc943e_chunk_13</data>
      <data key="d14">92822355-ab82-4e40-9fca-0876f2fc943e</data>
