      <data key="d8">ACH OF APPROXIMATELY 36</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_ACH</data>
      <data key="d10">The test room had an estimated ventilation rate of approximately 36 air changes per hour, based on 2068 CFM of measured supply airflow and a room volume of 3,405 ft3.</data>
