      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">Indoor mass gatherings increase opportunities for SARS-CoV-2 transmission because many people share the same indoor environment and may have close contacts. | Indoor mass gathering events concentrate visitors and contacts, increasing opportunities for SARS-CoV-2 exposure and transmission in the modeled scenarios.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.86</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d_chunk_0</data>
      <data key="d14">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d</data>
