      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2 (COVID-19)</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">Indoor mass gatherings can increase SARS-CoV-2 transmission by adding contacts and shared indoor exposure, but the text emphasizes that under precautions they usually contribute only a small fraction of new cases.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.68</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d_chunk_13</data>
      <data key="d14">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d</data>
    </edge>
