      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">An indoor professional sporting event represents a crowded indoor occupancy scenario where SARS-CoV-2 transmission was specifically referenced in the related content.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.65</data>
