      <data key="d8">INFECTIOUS AEROSOLS</data>
      <data key="d9">ACH_AFFECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The weak upward flow in VV2 failed to effectively remove infectious aerosols toward the roof, contributing to greater exposure.</data>
