      <data key="d9">HAS_DISTRIBUTION_PATTERN</data>
      <data key="d10">The solid grandstands were among the occupied areas where exposure was evaluated, and the direct mouth-to-mouth aerosol mechanism was described as occurring irrespective of position.</data>
