      <data key="d8">INFECTIOUS AEROSOLS</data>
      <data key="d9">ACH_AFFECTS</data>
      <data key="d10">The low ACH of 0.85 h−1 affected infectious aerosol exposure by reducing dilution and removal, contributing to the larger number of exposed individuals under VV2.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.96</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d_chunk_8</data>
      <data key="d14">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d</data>
