    <edge source="EXPOSED VISITORS IN VV1" target="SARS-COV-2">
      <data key="d7">EXPOSED VISITORS IN VV1</data>
      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The exposed visitor load in VV1 represents the modeled number of occupants exposed to SARS-CoV-2. Reported lower values under hygiene scenarios indicate reduced exposure burden in this occupancy group. | The exposed visitor load in VV2 represents occupants exposed to SARS-CoV-2, with higher mean exposed-visitor counts than VV1 under the reported hygiene scenarios.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.62</data>
      <data key="d12">2</data>
      <data key="d13">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d_chunk_9</data>
      <data key="d14">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d</data>
    </edge>
