      <data key="d8">SARS-COV-2</data>
      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">The presence or introduction of SARS-CoV-2 positive individuals, including visitors from higher-incidence regions, can increase opportunities for SARS-CoV-2 transmission during indoor events.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.76</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
      <data key="d13">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d_chunk_9</data>
      <data key="d14">0676edf9-1d10-4220-bdea-1b4729f9856d</data>
