      <data key="d9">OCCUPANCY_INCREASES</data>
      <data key="d10">Vocalization is discussed as producing more respiratory particles than breathing. If singers are infectious, this higher particle generation can increase potential airborne SARS-CoV-2 emission into the surrounding air.</data>
